19#include "PDFModulusPoly.h"
20
21#include <stdexcept>
22
23namespace ZXing {
24namespace Pdf417 {
25
26/**
27* <p>A field based on powers of a generator integer, modulo some modulus.< / p>
28*
29* @author Sean Owen
30* @see com.google.zxing.common.reedsolomon.GenericGF
31*/
32class ModulusGF
33{
34 int _modulus;
35 std::vector<int> _expTable;
36 std::vector<int> _logTable;
37 ModulusPoly _zero;
38 ModulusPoly _one;
39
40public:
41 ModulusGF(int modulus, int generator);
42
43 const ModulusPoly& zero() const {
44 return _zero;
45 }
46
47 const ModulusPoly& one() const {
48 return _one;
49 }
50
51 ModulusPoly buildMonomial(int degree, int coefficient) const;
52
53 int add(int a, int b) const {
54 return (a + b) % _modulus;
55 }
56
57 int subtract(int a, int b) const {
58 return (_modulus + a - b) % _modulus;
59 }
60
61 int exp(int a) const {
62 return _expTable.at(a);
63 }
64
65 int log(int a) const {
66 if (a == 0) {
67 throw std::invalid_argument("a == 0");
68 }
69 return _logTable[a];
70 }
71
72 int inverse(int a) const {
73 if (a == 0) {
74 throw std::invalid_argument("a == 0");
75 }
76 return _expTable[_modulus - _logTable[a] - 1];
77 }
78
79 int multiply(int a, int b) const {
80 if (a == 0 || b == 0) {
81 return 0;
82 }
83 return _expTable[(_logTable[a] + _logTable[b]) % (_modulus - 1)];
84 }
85
86 int size() const {
87 return _modulus;
88 }
89};
90
91} // Pdf417
92} // ZXing
